title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Tools & Cutlery of Base Met
description: Imports of Intra EU - Tools & Cutlery of Base Met in the United Kingdom decreased to 49.42 GBP Million in September from 58.37 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Tools & Cutlery of Base Met in the United Kingdom averaged 45.69 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 98.61 GBP Million in August of 2017 and a record low of 20.28 GBP Million in December of 1996. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Tools & Cutlery of Base Met.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
